<subSubSection id="C36B652A810CFFA0FF31FC22FEB0FBEE" pageId="35" pageNumber="36" type="distribution">
<paragraph id="8BCE36A1810CFFA0FF31FC22FD30FC7E" blockId="35.[136,1452,806,1084]" box="[189,643,914,941]" pageId="35" pageNumber="36">
<emphasis id="B905EAB3810CFFA0FF31FC22FEC6FC7E" bold="true" box="[189,373,914,940]" pageId="35" pageNumber="36">Distribution:—</emphasis>
<collectingCountry id="F3667631810CFFA0FEF9FC23FE51FC7F" box="[373,482,915,941]" name="Myanmar" pageId="35" pageNumber="36">Myanmar</collectingCountry>
and 
<collectingCountry id="F3667631810CFFA0FD94FC22FDCCFC7E" box="[536,639,914,940]" name="Thailand" pageId="35" pageNumber="36">Thailand</collectingCountry>
.
</paragraph>
<paragraph id="8BCE36A1810CFFA0FF31FC06FEB0FBEE" blockId="35.[136,1452,806,1084]" pageId="35" pageNumber="36">
<emphasis id="B905EAB3810CFFA0FF31FC06FEA8FC02" bold="true" box="[189,283,950,976]" pageId="35" pageNumber="36">Note:—</emphasis>
Previously 
<bibRefCitation id="EFE04B50810CFFA0FE15FC06FD1FFC02" author="Seidenfaden, G." box="[409,684,950,976]" pageId="35" pageNumber="36" pagination="1 - 228" refId="ref228148" refString="Seidenfaden, G. (1979) Orchid genera in Thailand VIII. Bulbophyllum Thouars. Dansk Botanisk Arkiv 33 (3): 1 - 228." type="journal article" year="1979">Seidenfaden (1979: 122)</bibRefCitation>
noted that two plants probably belonging to this species are mounted on the 
<typeStatus id="54CA8803810CFFA0FF55FC6BFEBAFC27" box="[217,265,987,1013]" pageId="35" pageNumber="36">type</typeStatus>
sheet of the 
<collectingCountry id="F3667631810CFFA0FE2EFC6BFDBCFC27" box="[418,527,987,1013]" name="Myanmar" pageId="35" pageNumber="36">Myanmar</collectingCountry>
endemic 
<taxonomicName id="4C714D22810CFFA0FD0DFC6AFC1EFC26" authority="Bull" authorityName="Bull" box="[641,941,986,1012]" class="Liliopsida" family="Orchidaceae" genus="Bulbophyllum" kingdom="Plantae" order="Asparagales" pageId="35" pageNumber="36" phylum="Tracheophyta" rank="species" species="pechei">
<emphasis id="B905EAB3810CFFA0FD0DFC6AFCC2FC26" box="[641,881,986,1012]" italics="true" pageId="35" pageNumber="36">Bulbophyllum pechei</emphasis>
Bull
</taxonomicName>
, suggesting that 
<taxonomicName id="4C714D22810CFFA0FBFCFC6BFAB5FC26" box="[1136,1286,987,1012]" class="Liliopsida" family="Orchidaceae" genus="Bulbophyllum" kingdom="Plantae" order="Asparagales" pageId="35" pageNumber="36" phylum="Tracheophyta" rank="species" species="intricatum">
<emphasis id="B905EAB3810CFFA0FBFCFC6BFAB5FC26" box="[1136,1286,987,1012]" italics="true" pageId="35" pageNumber="36">B. intricatum</emphasis>
</taxonomicName>
should not be considered endemic to 
<collectingCountry id="F3667631810CFFA0FE1EFC4EFE4BFBCA" box="[402,504,1022,1048]" name="Thailand" pageId="35" pageNumber="36">Thailand</collectingCountry>
, which it was at the time, but has “a more western distribution”. This can now be confirmed.
</paragraph>
